title: Reflexive Defender of the Crown Heroes Live Forever - RaBBiT
description:
Defender of the Crown: Heroes Live Forever

Battle five cunning lords for control of medieval England! Build and lead your armies of knights and archers on the battlefield, and conduct daring raids to rescue princesses and pillage treasuries. Compete in jousting and archery tournaments, and lay siege to your foes with catapults and Greek Fire! Gain fame, outsmart, and out muscle your foes to lay sole claim to the British crown!
